{"id": "1410995709305421854", "channel_id": "1410995709305421854", "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "content": "With the amount of entries that Archive has, it is very time consuming to click onto every single one of them, in order to get the „new“ message for the Archive icon in the main menu to leave. Having a „seen all“ or „read all“ button that just allows you to mark everything as seen (like we have in the „Notice“ menu (pic for reference)) would be helpful to finally have that „new“ message gone instead of for having to click on every single thing that is in the archives.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T14:33:12.131000+00:00", "thread_id": "1410995709305421854", "attachments": [{"id": "1410995709699817544", "filename": "IMG_6049.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 955941, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1410995709305421854/1410995709699817544/IMG_6049.png?ex=69cbdb28&is=69ca89a8&hm=b67dfb4870d92ca63697efbb1a89408674700874a024113fd1c6ceb5577642c1&"}]}
