{"id": "1411083473481105448", "channel_id": "1411083473481105448", "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "content": "I copied Ericas \"Mechanical Barrier\" with Echoed Simulation and it didn't do anything, I got no additional stacks of Taunt nor of Fortress. \nI have not done any testing with other cards so I only know of this faulty interaction. If this interaction is intended as such, then Echoed Simulation should not be able to copy Mechanical Barrier and other cards that it shouldn't be able to interact with, and Echoed Simulation should explain what can and cannot be copied. But I suppose this is just a faulty interaction instead so i will report it as a bug.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T20:21:56.741000+00:00", "thread_id": "1411083473481105448", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-29T20:22:40.862000+00:00"}
